  lines:
  - speakerName: Boss
    portrait: {fileID: 1984190853, guid: 1be9303cf68adf8469a107b28073a96a, type: 3}
    text: Still not working... The GPU wasn't the only problem.
    showOnRightSide: 0
  - speakerName: Boss
    portrait: {fileID: 1984190853, guid: 1be9303cf68adf8469a107b28073a96a, type: 3}
    text: The symptom changed though — that tells us something.
    showOnRightSide: 0
  - speakerName: Boss
    portrait: {fileID: 1984190853, guid: 1be9303cf68adf8469a107b28073a96a, type: 3}
    text: When one swap doesn't fix it, move to the next suspect.
    showOnRightSide: 0
